name: DFDS Seaways Commodore De Luxe Cabin
descr:
Commodore Class De-Luxe cabin with balcony or private jaccuzzi?

Our very best cabins see the Commodore de Luxe Class. Commodore Balcony has a private balcony and Owners Suite is available with or without jaccuzzi. You also get access to the exclusive Commodore De Luxe Lounge throughout the trip.
